# Features Module Directory
#
# This directory contains self-contained business feature modules.
# Each feature should be independent and not import from other features.
#
# Build Map v2.1 ENHANCED compliance:
# - Features are self-contained modules
# - Use core services through dependency injection
# - Compose shared components for UI needs
# - Follow single responsibility principle
#
# Architecture boundaries:
# - Features can import: @core/*, @components/*, standard libraries
# - Features cannot import: @features/*, app, lib layers, other features
# - Features should not cross-communicate directly
# - Use core services for data operations
#
# Example feature structure:
# features/
# ├── user-management/
# │   ├── components/         - Feature-specific components
# │   ├── services/          - Feature business logic (extends CoreService)
# │   ├── types/             - Feature-specific types
# │   ├── hooks/             - Feature-specific hooks
# │   └── index.ts           - Feature public API
# ├── listings/
# │   ├── components/
# │   ├── services/
# │   └── ...
# └── dashboard/
#     ├── components/
#     ├── services/
#     └── ...
#
# Feature isolation principles:
# - Features expose public APIs through index.ts
# - Features use core services for shared functionality
# - Features compose shared components for consistent UI
# - Features handle their own state management
# - Features define their own types and interfaces
#
# BUILD_V5.0 P1 Service Foundation - Features ready for implementation ✓